AsyncStatus is a List
    is primary
    title is "_"
    single select
    show as simple list
    suppress standard toolbar
    Display Fields
        ID
            left align
            bold
        Status
            display as tag
                color of red when (RedAlertStatus)
                color of green when (Status.Running)
                color of yellow when (Status.Suspended)
        Message
            display as tag
                color of blue when (ID.CurrentlyRunning)
                color of purple when (ID.TotalQueued)
                color of green when (ID.TotalFinished)
                color of red when (ID.TotalFailed)
            raise yellow alert when (WarningState)
    open action is restricted
